      <h2>Why buy a Visitor Pass?</h2>
<ul>
    <li>You can buy a 2 Day or 3 Day Visitor Pass for unlimited off-peak travel in <a href="http://content.tfl.gov.uk/standard-tube-map.pdf">Zones 1-6</a></li>
    <li>You don't need to pre-order, you can buy your Visitor Pass at a number of Tube stations and Visitor Centres across London, or you can buy it one week in advance from Visitor Centres</li>
    <li>You don't need to top up your Visitor Pass, once you've bought it, you can travel as much as you want</li>
    <li>If you're <a href="/travel-information/visiting-london/getting-to-london/london-airports">travelling to London from Heathrow Airport</a>, your Visitor Pass is valid for travel on TfL Rail to Paddington station</li>
</ul>
