<h2>Off-peak travel </h2>
<p>Your Visitor Pass is only valid for off-peak travel which starts from 09:30 Monday to Friday, and for journeys starting before 04:30 the following day. It's also valid anytime on Saturdays, Sundays and bank holidays. </p>
<p>You can travel in Zones 1-6 on each day from the start date printed on your pass, to the expiry date.</p>
<p>Your Visitor Pass isn't valid for travel, or to buy discounted fares on National Rail, <a href="/modes/emirates-air-line/index">Emirates Air Line</a> or <a href="/modes/river/about-river-bus">River Bus services</a>.</p>

 
